'''加兹尼机场'''（{{airport codes|GZI|OAGN}}）是一座位于[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]东部[[加兹尼省|加兹尼省]][[加兹尼|加兹尼]]的机场，机场紧邻[[喀布尔–坎大哈公路|喀布尔–坎大哈公路]] <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://goo.gl/maps/1IgrN |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-08 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117145244/https://www.google.com/maps?q=Ghazni+Airport&hl=en&ll=33.538032,68.425941&spn=0.037416,0.084543&sll=33.536101,68.430147&sspn=0.037417,0.084543&t=h&z=14 }}</ref>。机场的服务对象主要是加兹尼省及[[阿富汗行政区划|附近省份]]的人口。该机场自2013年晚些时候开始有民用航班运营，并在不断发展当中<ref name=PAN>{{cite news | url = http://www.pajhwok.com/en/2013/12/28/7m-ghazni-civil-airport-inaugurated | title = $7m Ghazni civil airport inaugurated | publisher = [[Pajhwok_Afghan_News|Pajhwok Afghan News]] | date = 28 December 2013 | accessdate = 28 December 2013 | first = Saifullah | last = Maftoon | archive-date = 2016-06-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160602190412/http://www.pajhwok.com/en/2013/12/28/7m-ghazni-civil-airport-inaugurated | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==历史==
以前这里是一座[[军用机场|军用机场]]，在[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|阿富汗战争]]之后，阿富汗政府决定将这里改建成为一座国际机场。 机场拥有一条方向为15/33，长度为{{convert|1000|ft|0}}的跑道<ref name="MOTCA" />。政府计划兴建两条飞机跑道，原预计整个工程于2014年完成<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.pajhwok.com/en/2013/07/02/work-ghazni-airport-launched | title = Work on Ghazni airport launched | publisher = Pajhwok Afghan News | date = 2 July 2013 | accessdate = 5 July 2013 | first = Saifullah | last = Maftoon | archive-date = 2016-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009201139/http://www.pajhwok.com/en/2013/07/02/work-ghazni-airport-launched | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2013年12月底时，一个小型私人航空公司的飞机在加兹尼机场降落，标志着机场的改建一期工程完成<ref name=PAN/>。

